= SDL_GetWindowPosition =
Use this function to get the position of the window.


== Syntax ==
```c++
void SDL_GetWindowPosition(SDL_Window window,
                           int*        x,
                           int*        y)
```

== Function Parameters ==
{|
|'''window'''
|the type used to identify the window
|-
|'''x'''
|a pointer to the x coordinate of the window
|-
|'''y'''
|a pointer to the y coordinate of the window
|}

